Type: Package
Package: myCubeR
Title: Customization of the R-package "CubeR" (Author Mattia Rossi, mattia.rossi@eurac.edu) to access to 'ARPA LOMBARDIA Rasdaman database' via WCS and WCPS queries
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
  person("Mattia", "Rossi", email="mattia.rossi@eurac.edu", role=c("aut", "cre")),
  person("Susanna", "Grasso", email="s.grasso@arpalombardia.it", role="aut"))
Description: This package provides core functionalities 
  to access data cubes or geospatial timeseries with WCS and WCPS queries. 
  This Packages is tested with the Rasdaman Implementation of ARPA LOMBARDIA.
